WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 21=

01:40.850 --> 01:41.900
I've told Lingbo.

01:42.230 --> 01:43.570
I'll call off the engagement
when back.

01:49.850 --> 01:50.690
That's so sudden.

01:51.340 --> 01:52.260
Lingbo, she...

01:52.290 --> 01:53.210
It's not her fault.

01:54.540 --> 01:55.740
Just mine.

01:57.980 --> 01:58.820
Zhao.

02:02.290 --> 02:03.130
I...

02:03.140 --> 02:05.770
I'm drunk and free with the breeze.

02:06.050 --> 02:06.980
Xingjia.

02:08.980 --> 02:09.890
What are you up to?

02:10.920 --> 02:12.410
Isn't the sacrificial rite in two days?

02:12.410 --> 02:13.660
I'm preparing some offerings.

02:13.660 --> 02:15.660
Three vegetarian fruits
and three vegetarian pastries.

02:15.660 --> 02:16.500
Six varieties in total.

02:17.450 --> 02:18.320
Oh, right.

02:18.340 --> 02:19.290
The cemetery is cold.

02:19.290 --> 02:20.540
Remember to wear more.

02:28.060 --> 02:33.620
(Chang Cemetery)

02:37.010 --> 02:37.850
Zhao.

02:39.500 --> 02:41.780
Zhao, you also think the Jade Sunflower

02:41.780 --> 02:43.540
is hidden within the Chang Cemetery?

02:44.780 --> 02:45.660
You and I

02:46.260 --> 02:47.730
truly share the same thoughts.

02:48.850 --> 02:49.690
Zhao.

02:51.890 --> 02:53.540
Yuzhi, why are you here too?

02:53.980 --> 02:54.820
I told you

02:55.290 --> 02:56.690
I'd look out for you from now on.

02:59.100 --> 03:00.410
Zhao has me. That's enough.

03:01.410 --> 03:03.060
No need for Song to trouble yourself.

03:05.730 --> 03:07.380
The letter I sent you,

03:07.380 --> 03:08.380
you showed it to him as well?

03:08.980 --> 03:10.410
Zhao is here to help me

03:10.410 --> 03:11.780
find the Jade Sunflower.

03:12.610 --> 03:13.940
May I ask why

03:14.570 --> 03:15.500
Mr. Mu is here?

03:15.690 --> 03:17.170
Where Zhao goes, I go.

03:18.410 --> 03:19.410
What Zhao does,

03:20.260 --> 03:21.340
I do.

03:22.010 --> 03:23.130
Both of you, leave now.

03:36.340 --> 03:37.690
Since you're done arguing,

03:38.340 --> 03:40.290
stay and talk sense.

03:41.540 --> 03:42.570
Mu Qingyan,

03:42.570 --> 03:43.820
why did you suspect

03:43.820 --> 03:44.850
the Jade Sunflower

03:44.850 --> 03:46.290
was hidden in the Chang Cemetery?

03:46.290 --> 03:47.660
Nie Zhe's men

03:47.660 --> 03:50.100
searched every corner of the Chang Fort,

03:50.100 --> 03:51.820
yet they didn't find it.

03:51.820 --> 03:53.220
After thinking it over,

03:53.220 --> 03:54.500
it seemed only the cemetery

03:54.500 --> 03:56.500
was the one place
they might have overlooked.

03:56.500 --> 03:58.500
So I got some brothers
who're good at digging graves.

03:59.820 --> 04:01.850
Mr. Mu's brilliant idea

04:01.850 --> 04:02.890
is to dig up graves?

04:02.890 --> 04:04.380
If we don't dig,

04:04.380 --> 04:06.340
does Song have a better plan?

04:06.850 --> 04:07.850
Enough.

04:10.730 --> 04:11.940
Over a decade ago,

04:11.940 --> 04:13.380
my Dad brought me here.

04:19.100 --> 04:19.940
You two

04:19.960 --> 04:21.220
joined Chang in ancestor worship.

04:21.220 --> 04:22.340
How did you both get sunburned?

04:22.730 --> 04:23.850
But I've been here twice

04:24.900 --> 04:26.140
and didn't find any

04:26.140 --> 04:27.340
sunny spots.

04:42.340 --> 04:43.980
Could the problem be
with this stone pillar?

04:44.540 --> 04:45.730
Then let's just topple it.

04:45.730 --> 04:46.570
I'll call someone now.

04:48.290 --> 04:49.250
Wait.

04:53.490 --> 04:54.330
Don't call anyone yet.

04:54.850 --> 04:56.340
Does Zhao want to stay here

04:56.780 --> 04:59.100
searching with me forever?

04:59.610 --> 05:00.540
Mr. Mu,

05:01.370 --> 05:02.490
please mind your manners.

05:09.630 --> 05:10.620
Let's get down to business.

05:11.290 --> 05:14.170
So the mirror surface
is what gave me sunburn.

05:14.170 --> 05:15.220
The back mountain is shaded.

05:15.220 --> 05:16.410
Sunlight's scarce.

05:16.410 --> 05:17.900
Logically,

05:17.900 --> 05:20.290
it shouldn't burn anyone.

05:21.900 --> 05:23.490
But with this bronze mirror,

05:23.490 --> 05:25.290
the faint sunlight

05:25.290 --> 05:26.780
can be concentrated several times

05:26.780 --> 05:28.020
and reflected to the other side.

05:29.250 --> 05:31.050
But the stone pillar sank down.

05:31.050 --> 05:32.900
So both times,

05:32.900 --> 05:34.290
I avoided being burned.

05:34.980 --> 05:37.540
Wu'an Mountain is made of hard granite,

05:38.020 --> 05:39.140
with dense forests.

05:39.700 --> 05:41.490
Its foundation should be firm.

05:41.900 --> 05:44.340
It can't just sink for no reason.

05:44.980 --> 05:45.900
Unless...

05:45.900 --> 05:46.930
The ground below was hollowed.

05:48.020 --> 05:49.610
Do you remember

05:49.610 --> 05:51.220
the Shi brothers,
my aunt's good friends?

05:51.220 --> 05:53.290
The second Shi brother
was struck by Nether Aura.

05:53.780 --> 05:55.100
But your aunt cured him later.

05:55.610 --> 05:56.660
That's why

05:56.660 --> 05:58.250
you're looking for
the Jade Sunflower for him.

06:02.930 --> 06:04.170
Are the Shi brothers

06:04.730 --> 06:05.980
tomb raiders by trade?

06:09.540 --> 06:10.490
The Shi brothers

06:10.490 --> 06:12.660
gave my aunt
some family heirlooms before.

06:12.660 --> 06:15.170
As a child, I'd flip through them
out of boredom.

06:15.930 --> 06:17.370
Inside, it was all records of

06:17.370 --> 06:20.140
the skills and methods
for building subterranean tombs.

06:20.140 --> 06:23.100
Don't think constructing
a subterranean tomb is easy.

06:23.100 --> 06:24.370
You must guard against water seepage.

06:24.370 --> 06:26.250
And against rats, insects,
snakes, and ants.

06:26.250 --> 06:27.340
After sealing the entrance,

06:27.340 --> 06:28.980
you must leave no trace behind.

06:28.980 --> 06:30.290
There are so many tricks to it.

06:38.780 --> 06:40.170
South is Li. North is Kan.

06:40.730 --> 06:42.170
Kan is one. Qian is six.

06:42.440 --> 06:43.850
Kun, in the southwest, commands the yin.

06:44.660 --> 06:47.050
Align with the cycles of life and death.

06:48.290 --> 06:49.340
The entrance is right here.

06:49.340 --> 06:50.180
- Alright.
- Alright.

06:50.190 --> 06:51.310
- Miss Cai decides.
- Zhao leads.

07:27.340 --> 07:28.540
Miss Cai.

07:28.540 --> 07:30.810
Does this wall have

07:31.900 --> 07:32.900
any meaning in tomb lore?

07:33.290 --> 07:34.250
It's the Turnback Wall.

07:34.630 --> 07:36.100
A signature skill of the Shi brothers.

07:36.900 --> 07:38.250
The mechanism should be nearby.

07:53.020 --> 07:54.490
Do we need a key?

08:02.100 --> 08:03.170
You actually have one?

08:07.660 --> 08:08.500
There's no keyhole.

08:10.610 --> 08:11.450
Lock latch?

08:22.780 --> 08:23.850
Where'd that come from?

08:23.850 --> 08:25.250
Mr. Chang left it to me.

08:25.460 --> 08:26.730
Back then, Jiang Ning changed his tone.

08:27.170 --> 08:28.410
Only after seeing this.

08:28.780 --> 08:30.580
Uncle Chang truly trusts you.

08:58.770 --> 08:59.700
Light the lamps first.

09:10.780 --> 09:13.060
(Memorial tablet of Lu Chengnan
from the Li Sect)

09:13.580 --> 09:15.130
Lu Chengnan is really dead.

09:16.530 --> 09:18.220
This looks like my aunt's handwriting.

09:22.130 --> 09:23.250
Sun rises. Moon sets.

09:23.890 --> 09:25.820
You've always walked alone.

09:25.820 --> 09:27.530
Both bold and noble.

09:27.530 --> 09:29.700
Lofty mountains and flowing rivers.

09:29.700 --> 09:31.730
Lord, as you depart.

09:31.730 --> 09:33.420
May your journey be free of obstacles.

09:41.300 --> 09:43.610
This tomb was built by the Shi brothers.

09:43.610 --> 09:45.250
It bears my aunt's own handwriting.

09:46.010 --> 09:47.580
Could Lu Chengnan

09:47.580 --> 09:48.770
really be a skin-painted demon?

09:49.370 --> 09:51.580
Though he was from the Li Sect,

09:51.580 --> 09:53.130
he received such honor.

09:53.130 --> 09:54.060
Could

09:54.060 --> 09:55.300
he have been a righteous man?

09:55.300 --> 09:56.180
Let's find

09:56.700 --> 09:57.650
the Jade Sunflower first.

10:13.610 --> 10:14.530
Could it be

10:15.010 --> 10:16.340
in this stone coffin?

10:19.100 --> 10:19.940
Wait.

10:21.250 --> 10:22.090
Elder.

10:22.580 --> 10:23.420
Sorry to interrupt.

10:27.820 --> 10:28.770
Not inside.

10:32.060 --> 10:33.180
Sternum shattered,

10:33.700 --> 10:35.370
surrounding bones cracked.

10:35.370 --> 10:37.060
Even the underarm ribs are broken.

10:37.060 --> 10:38.300
Nie Hengcheng's signature move.

10:39.010 --> 10:40.490
Soulreaving Cloud Palm.

10:40.490 --> 10:42.130
Elder Yan's words were all true.

10:42.130 --> 10:44.300
Nie Hengcheng really killed Lu Chengnan.

10:44.940 --> 10:46.490
What's so mysterious

10:46.490 --> 10:48.100
about the Jade Sunflower?

10:48.100 --> 10:49.010
Nie Hengcheng

10:49.010 --> 10:51.370
killed his favorite disciple for it.

10:51.370 --> 10:52.940
Nie Zhe and the Man in Black

10:52.940 --> 10:54.060
massacred

10:54.060 --> 10:56.010
Uncle Chang's entire family for it.

10:56.010 --> 10:57.530
Once we find the Jade Sunflower,

10:57.530 --> 10:58.700
everything will be clear.

10:59.220 --> 11:00.180
Maybe

11:01.060 --> 11:03.010
we can ask the tomb builders.

11:03.010 --> 11:04.890
But the Shi brothers have retired.

11:04.890 --> 11:06.010
My Master and Father

11:06.010 --> 11:07.940
don't even know

11:07.940 --> 11:09.060
where they are.

11:10.980 --> 11:12.250
Let's get out first and talk.

11:17.820 --> 11:18.730
Don't move.

11:19.420 --> 11:20.300
Otherwise,

11:20.300 --> 11:21.850
they all die.

11:36.890 --> 11:37.730
Nie Zhe.

11:38.060 --> 11:39.700
If you dare harm them,

11:39.700 --> 11:41.610
the Six Sects will hunt you down

11:41.610 --> 11:42.890
to the last person!

11:43.490 --> 11:44.340
Cai Zhao.

11:44.340 --> 11:45.610
We didn't come to

11:46.180 --> 11:47.820
be enemies with the Six Sects.

11:48.130 --> 11:49.940
Just hand over the Jade Sunflower,

11:49.940 --> 11:51.890
and we'll let them go.

11:52.250 --> 11:53.850
What do you think, Mr. Mu?

11:54.200 --> 11:55.650
You seized people from the Six Sects.

11:56.420 --> 11:57.820
What has that to do with me?

11:59.010 --> 12:01.700
They're all kin
to the leaders of the Six Sects.

12:02.250 --> 12:03.770
If they die,

12:03.770 --> 12:05.580
Six Sects and Li Sect are going to war.

12:05.580 --> 12:06.820
By then,

12:06.820 --> 12:08.490
can you still hold onto

12:09.340 --> 12:10.940
your position as Young Master?

12:11.300 --> 12:12.340
So what?

12:14.180 --> 12:15.340
Fine, fine.

12:17.610 --> 12:18.450
Wait!

12:23.300 --> 12:24.140
Hand it over.

12:28.060 --> 12:28.900
Hand it over!

12:42.490 --> 12:43.370
Here, take it.

12:53.370 --> 12:54.220
Strategist!

12:55.100 --> 12:56.770
My face! My face!

12:56.770 --> 12:58.130
Someone! Hurry!

13:06.430 --> 13:07.580
Get the strategist out first!

13:07.580 --> 13:08.420
Hurry!

13:51.430 --> 13:53.060
The softening powder's effects
are gone now.

13:53.060 --> 13:54.370
Stay hydrated for the next two days.

13:54.370 --> 13:55.210
I won't drink!

14:05.730 --> 14:07.300
Teaming up with Mu Qingyan this time

14:07.300 --> 14:08.850
was indeed my own decision.

14:09.420 --> 14:11.180
But Nie Zhe is lurking nearby,

14:11.180 --> 14:12.610
and if we don't draw him out now,

14:12.610 --> 14:13.940
no one knows when he'll surface again.

14:14.850 --> 14:16.180
That softening powder everyone got.

14:16.180 --> 14:18.220
Master You tested its effects
beforehand.

14:18.220 --> 14:19.770
I kept this from everyone,

14:19.770 --> 14:21.940
because Nie Zhe's spies
are near the inn.

14:21.940 --> 14:23.420
You could have hidden it from us,

14:23.420 --> 14:24.820
so why tell Cai Zhao?

14:25.370 --> 14:26.490
Lingbo,

14:26.490 --> 14:28.420
I only found out

14:28.420 --> 14:29.820
right before you arrived.

14:30.820 --> 14:31.850
Yuzhi,

14:31.850 --> 14:33.850
when did you arrange this
with Mu Qingyan?

14:35.300 --> 14:38.180
Since Nie Zhe is so fixated on
the Jade Sunflower,

14:38.180 --> 14:39.850
why not use this chance to lure him out?

14:40.490 --> 14:42.580
I'm sure you feel the same.

14:42.580 --> 14:43.890
Nie Zhe is cunning and suspicious.

14:44.620 --> 14:46.060
If we want to force him to show himself,

14:47.880 --> 14:49.490
we'll need to offer him
something tempting.

14:53.060 --> 14:54.580
Didn't expect you two guys

14:54.580 --> 14:55.940
have little secrets.

14:57.180 --> 14:58.130
Cai Zhao.

14:58.130 --> 15:00.130
It's bad enough
you're tangled up with Mu Qingyan.

15:00.580 --> 15:01.940
Why must you drag Yuzhi into this too?

15:02.220 --> 15:03.420
Me and Mu Qingyan.

15:04.010 --> 15:05.250
How exactly are we tangled up?

15:05.250 --> 15:07.770
Young Lord Zhou isn't here right now,
drop the act.

15:08.420 --> 15:10.530
You clearly like Mu Qingyan.

15:10.720 --> 15:12.890
You two were close
back when you were in Qingque Sect.

15:13.240 --> 15:15.220
So why would he have followed you
all the way to the inn?

15:15.940 --> 15:16.780
Speaking of which,

15:17.520 --> 15:18.650
someone from your Luoying Valley

15:18.650 --> 15:20.980
fraternized with the demon sect before.

15:21.420 --> 15:22.610
Some habits just never change!

15:24.370 --> 15:26.100
Insult me all you want.

15:26.100 --> 15:27.770
But don't you dare
insult Luoying Valley.

15:27.770 --> 15:29.060
I'll say it!

15:29.060 --> 15:30.130
Lingbo.

15:30.130 --> 15:31.940
Nie Zhe is the murderer
of the Chang clan.

15:31.940 --> 15:33.060
Teaming up with Mu Qingyan

15:33.060 --> 15:34.370
to catch him was a necessary compromise.

15:34.370 --> 15:36.490
Besides, the idea of cooperation
came from me.

15:36.490 --> 15:37.420
Zhao's out of it.

15:39.820 --> 15:40.770
Miss Cai.

15:43.020 --> 15:44.420
Young Master requests your presence.

15:45.980 --> 15:46.820
Alright.

15:47.580 --> 15:49.010
No more hiding.

15:49.010 --> 15:49.850
Cai Zhao.

15:50.420 --> 15:51.580
Don't forget

15:51.980 --> 15:53.730
you have a fiancé.

15:56.300 --> 15:57.140
Why does he want me?

15:57.340 --> 15:58.300
Elder Hu has confessed.

15:58.300 --> 16:00.340
He also asks Mr. Song to come.

16:00.340 --> 16:01.420
You Guanyue.

16:01.980 --> 16:03.940
Can't you say it all at once?

16:03.940 --> 16:04.790
Miss Cai.

16:04.800 --> 16:06.100
The Young Master asks you to come.

16:06.100 --> 16:07.010
Elder Hu has confessed.

16:07.010 --> 16:09.420
Mr. Song is also invited.

16:17.340 --> 16:19.980
The mastermind you've been looking for

16:21.820 --> 16:23.530
is one of the Six Sects.

16:24.130 --> 16:24.970
Elder Hu.

16:26.300 --> 16:28.370
That mysterious man
moved freely in the Li Sect.

16:28.370 --> 16:29.820
He's clearly one of the Li Sect.

16:29.820 --> 16:31.530
Why spout nonsense

16:31.530 --> 16:32.490
and stir up trouble?

16:32.980 --> 16:34.340
Believe it or not, it's up to you.

16:34.940 --> 16:36.370
But you Six Sects

16:37.100 --> 16:38.130
have done plenty of

16:38.580 --> 16:39.890
self-deceptive things.

16:40.420 --> 16:41.260
You...

16:52.600 --> 16:54.130
Do you also think
it's one of the Six Sects?

16:54.130 --> 16:55.370
Earlier, the Six Sects were attacked,

16:56.420 --> 16:57.980
the mysterious man leaked

16:57.980 --> 16:59.820
everyone's whereabouts to Nie Zhe.

16:59.820 --> 17:01.370
Such confidential information.

17:01.370 --> 17:02.700
Besides the Six Sects' leaders,

17:02.700 --> 17:04.100
who else would know?

17:04.100 --> 17:04.980
Besides,

17:04.980 --> 17:06.700
I fought the Man in Black twice.

17:07.250 --> 17:08.380
His skill

17:08.380 --> 17:09.570
is unfathomable,

17:09.570 --> 17:11.010
no ordinary fighter.

17:11.660 --> 17:12.770
I think he's at

17:13.910 --> 17:14.850
Grandmaster level.

17:14.860 --> 17:16.360
Grandmaster level.

17:17.330 --> 17:19.250
Only the Six Sects' leaders

17:19.250 --> 17:20.660
reach this rank.

17:21.490 --> 17:22.330
My Master

17:22.470 --> 17:23.900
is already the Lord of the Six Sects.

17:24.330 --> 17:25.730
Why would he ally with Nie Zhe?

17:27.050 --> 17:28.330
Uncle Zhou's detached from fame,

17:28.330 --> 17:29.660
devoted to crafting weapons.

17:29.660 --> 17:30.770
No motive for this.

17:31.420 --> 17:33.220
The Taichu Temple
just changed leadership.

17:33.530 --> 17:35.330
As for Yang Heying of the Siqi Sect,

17:35.330 --> 17:36.420
he can't even beat me.

17:38.490 --> 17:39.380
And Lord Song.

17:39.380 --> 17:41.420
While it's plausible

17:41.420 --> 17:43.090
my father'd vie for
Lord of the Six Sects,

17:43.090 --> 17:44.420
colluding with the demon sect

17:44.420 --> 17:45.620
for ulterior motives?

17:45.620 --> 17:46.980
That's absolutely impossible.

17:46.980 --> 17:49.250
Exactly. Lord Song's pragmatic.

17:49.250 --> 17:51.140
For gains he can't see or touch,

17:51.140 --> 17:52.380
he wouldn't waste a single effort.

17:52.380 --> 17:53.220
Mr. Mu,

17:54.570 --> 17:56.420
you're not suspecting Mr. Cai, are you?

17:56.940 --> 17:57.980
Who the Man in Black is?

17:58.620 --> 17:59.730
Once we capture Nie Zhe alive,

18:00.050 --> 18:00.980
we'll know.

18:01.420 --> 18:02.260
Zhao,

18:02.730 --> 18:04.290
as long as we find the Jade Sunflower,

18:04.700 --> 18:05.770
he'll show himself.

18:06.380 --> 18:08.730
The Six Sects' leaders
can't be traitors.

18:08.730 --> 18:10.140
Even if secrets were leaked,

18:10.140 --> 18:12.180
it would only mean
Nie Zhe has a spy in the sects.

18:13.570 --> 18:14.410
Zhao.

18:14.620 --> 18:15.460
This is critical.

18:15.900 --> 18:17.490
We must return to the sect at once.

18:17.490 --> 18:18.330
And report to Master.

18:20.660 --> 18:22.090
Once we've honored Mr. Chang tomorrow,

18:22.700 --> 18:23.900
we'll set out back home.

18:34.730 --> 18:35.770
Zhao also thinks

18:36.180 --> 18:37.730
the mastermind is from the Six Sects?

18:39.900 --> 18:42.010
Not Master or the others, but...

18:42.010 --> 18:43.620
But you still have doubts.

18:44.190 --> 18:45.980
You think it might be
someone from the sects.

18:46.570 --> 18:47.900
Wasn't Mr. Wu

18:47.900 --> 18:49.730
killed by Qiu Yuanfeng?

18:49.730 --> 18:50.660
Qiu Yuanfeng

18:50.660 --> 18:51.940
was a former sect leader.

18:52.700 --> 18:54.700
Sometimes good and evil
hinge on a single thought.

18:55.140 --> 18:56.860
Whatever that figure is plotting,

18:57.810 --> 18:59.380
it's mostly

18:59.380 --> 19:00.570
tied to the Six Sects.

19:00.570 --> 19:02.250
Mr. Wu's case was an accident.

19:02.250 --> 19:03.620
Good and evil may be a thought apart,

19:04.180 --> 19:05.570
but the mastermind has planned

19:05.570 --> 19:06.490
for over ten years.

19:06.760 --> 19:08.250
This isn't a spur-of-the-moment thing.

19:08.250 --> 19:09.090
Besides,

19:09.810 --> 19:11.900
Hu Fengge is a demon sect elder.

19:11.900 --> 19:13.980
How credible is her testimony?

19:13.980 --> 19:15.570
Maybe her capture was a deliberate

19:16.090 --> 19:17.140
divide-and-conquer tactic.

19:17.420 --> 19:18.980
Since the key is the Jade Sunflower,

19:19.900 --> 19:21.380
then let's find it.

19:21.700 --> 19:24.490
Maybe then the truth will come to light.

19:24.490 --> 19:25.380
Besides, Yuzhi,

19:25.380 --> 19:26.860
you need it to dispel the cold.

19:26.860 --> 19:28.220
I can do without the Jade Sunflower.

19:28.660 --> 19:30.250
I'll just train harder from now on.

19:30.770 --> 19:31.610
Zhao,

19:32.570 --> 19:34.530
Mu Qingyan's identity
is common knowledge.

19:34.530 --> 19:36.090
No one can cover for us this time.

19:37.770 --> 19:38.770
Once we take this step,

19:40.140 --> 19:41.250
there's no turning back.

19:42.730 --> 19:43.570
I know.

19:43.700 --> 19:44.660
I'm at fault this time.

19:45.420 --> 19:46.980
I was too eager to
catch ringleader Nie Zhe,

19:46.980 --> 19:48.730
so I chose to work with Mu Qingyan.

19:48.730 --> 19:50.250
I not only put us in disrepute,

19:50.250 --> 19:51.730
but also endangered
Lingbo and the others.

19:52.290 --> 19:53.810
Don't mind

19:55.050 --> 19:56.010
what Lingbo said earlier.

19:57.140 --> 19:58.220
She's mad at me.

20:17.140 --> 20:17.980
Lingbo.

20:19.090 --> 20:20.220
Why are you here alone?

20:24.860 --> 20:25.770
Lingbo.

20:25.770 --> 20:26.610
What's wrong with you?

20:30.220 --> 20:31.940
Yuzhi was reckless this time.

20:32.660 --> 20:33.730
But I don't think

20:33.730 --> 20:35.050
Cai Zhao knew about it.

20:40.720 --> 20:41.810
He's calling off the engagement.

20:42.140 --> 20:43.380
Yuzhi's calling off the engagement?

20:43.810 --> 20:44.650
When?

20:44.900 --> 20:45.860
Yesterday.

20:46.660 --> 20:47.770
When we went to find him.

20:50.330 --> 20:51.290
Yuzhi, he...

20:55.050 --> 20:55.890
Lingbo.

20:56.700 --> 20:57.540
What

20:57.980 --> 20:59.570
do you truly think?

20:59.570 --> 21:00.530
I don't know.

21:03.140 --> 21:05.700
I grew up thinking
I'd marry Yuzhi.

21:06.290 --> 21:07.620
Now the engagement's off.

21:08.730 --> 21:10.730
I don't know what to do.

21:10.730 --> 21:11.730
Even with the engagement off,

21:12.490 --> 21:13.380
you're still you.

21:14.090 --> 21:15.180
You'll meet someone

21:15.180 --> 21:16.420
who truly likes you someday.

21:19.330 --> 21:20.170
Fengchi.

21:21.530 --> 21:22.380
Zhao.

21:24.380 --> 21:25.530
Let me be alone.

21:55.090 --> 21:55.930
Zhao.

21:57.220 --> 21:58.980
Xinrou's health hasn't recovered yet.

21:58.980 --> 21:59.900
Why did she come over?

22:06.420 --> 22:07.260
Have a seat.

22:12.490 --> 22:14.090
Thank you for the medicine, Zhao.

22:14.620 --> 22:16.140
I'm too weak.

22:16.140 --> 22:17.530
I've made everyone worry.

22:23.180 --> 22:24.090
This softening powder

22:24.090 --> 22:24.930
is truly potent.

22:25.290 --> 22:26.330
You have no inner power.

22:26.330 --> 22:28.770
So it should take ten to fifteen days

22:28.770 --> 22:29.770
for you to recover.

22:33.090 --> 22:33.930
Xinrou,

22:34.420 --> 22:35.810
why can't you stop coughing?

22:41.490 --> 22:42.380
Drink some water.

22:52.180 --> 22:53.940
If you knew you'd use softening powder,

22:54.620 --> 22:56.220
you should've at least
told us beforehand.

22:57.220 --> 22:59.090
Not everyone can endure that stuff.

23:00.530 --> 23:01.570
Zhao,

23:01.570 --> 23:02.660
after tomorrow's memorial,

23:03.050 --> 23:04.730
I'll send Xinrou back to Peiqiong Manor.

23:06.250 --> 23:07.620
As for the wedding date...

23:10.660 --> 23:11.500
What was that sound?

23:13.420 --> 23:15.290
Most likely that stray cat again.

23:15.290 --> 23:16.330
That stray cat again?

23:17.900 --> 23:19.570
That stray cat is truly a nuisance.

23:19.570 --> 23:20.410
I'll go have a look.

23:23.420 --> 23:24.900
I'll go deal with that stray cat.

23:28.380 --> 23:29.860
Zhao, you're so thoughtful.

23:30.810 --> 23:32.420
She's a true heroine.

23:33.530 --> 23:34.570
Unlike me,

23:35.490 --> 23:36.570
so useless.

23:44.420 --> 23:45.570
Why did you call me out here?

23:46.900 --> 23:47.980
Spit it out.

23:48.730 --> 23:50.290
If it's nothing important, I'm leaving.

23:51.010 --> 23:52.140
The matter between us,

23:52.860 --> 23:54.220
isn't that important too?

23:57.900 --> 23:59.380
Come with me to find the Shi brothers.

23:59.860 --> 24:01.330
Once we find the Shi brothers,

24:01.330 --> 24:03.090
we might learn
where the Jade Sunflower is.

24:03.090 --> 24:03.930
I'm not going.

24:05.700 --> 24:07.010
The Man in Black is too important.

24:07.380 --> 24:08.620
When I get back,

24:08.620 --> 24:10.490
I'll report everything to Master.

24:10.770 --> 24:11.770
What to do next

24:12.150 --> 24:13.620
will be decided by Master and others.

24:14.010 --> 24:14.850
Looks like

24:16.090 --> 24:17.940
your Master doesn't tell you everything.

24:18.380 --> 24:19.980
Don't you want to know

24:20.290 --> 24:21.660
if Lu Chengnan was

24:21.660 --> 24:23.010
your aunt's beloved?

24:23.730 --> 24:24.570
Or...

24:25.530 --> 24:26.490
the skin-painted demon?

24:27.140 --> 24:28.140
How did you find out?

24:28.660 --> 24:30.620
I've long suspected
your aunt loved another.

24:30.840 --> 24:33.090
Otherwise, she wouldn't have let
Lord Zhou marry another.

24:34.250 --> 24:35.620
If such a person truly exists,

24:36.090 --> 24:37.980
with your aunt's upright nature,

24:38.420 --> 24:40.980
she'd never let him hide till death.

24:41.620 --> 24:42.460
Unless,

24:43.010 --> 24:44.180
he's just like me,

24:45.380 --> 24:46.810
a member of the Li Sect.

24:47.620 --> 24:48.660
Why did your Master

24:48.660 --> 24:50.090
call me

24:50.090 --> 24:51.660
a skin-painted demon for no reason?

24:51.660 --> 24:53.700
It must be because there was once

24:54.700 --> 24:56.220
a skin-painted demon

24:56.980 --> 24:57.900
from the Li Sect.

25:00.900 --> 25:01.980
You're sharp.

25:02.900 --> 25:04.380
My aunt did have a beloved.

25:05.620 --> 25:06.940
But that person isn't Lu Chengnan.

25:08.380 --> 25:10.180
Yet the couplet
found in the ancient tomb

25:10.180 --> 25:11.980
was indeed written in her handwriting.

25:12.730 --> 25:13.860
That couplet

25:14.340 --> 25:15.940
doesn't read like
it was meant for a lover,

25:16.380 --> 25:17.660
but rather for someone...

25:17.660 --> 25:18.570
More like for a hero

25:19.010 --> 25:19.850
she admired,

25:20.380 --> 25:21.220
revered,

25:21.770 --> 25:23.330
and respected.

25:26.380 --> 25:27.220
Yes.

25:27.900 --> 25:29.050
But if Lu Chengnan

25:29.730 --> 25:31.570
wasn't the one your aunt loved,

25:32.620 --> 25:33.810
then who

25:34.660 --> 25:37.420
stole the Jade Sunflower
to heal the Shi brothers?

25:40.330 --> 25:41.330
So

25:42.050 --> 25:43.250
there's someone else

25:44.220 --> 25:46.250
in the demon sect
guiding your aunt.

25:46.900 --> 25:47.860
That person

25:48.220 --> 25:50.010
is the true skin-painted demon.

25:51.380 --> 25:52.220
Zhao.

25:52.810 --> 25:53.810
Come with me

25:54.940 --> 25:56.330
to find the Shi brothers.

25:57.010 --> 25:58.570
Only they

25:59.090 --> 26:00.380
hold the answers to all of this.

26:02.490 --> 26:04.770
But the Shi brothers
have lived in seclusion for years,

26:04.770 --> 26:06.380
how long will it take to find them?

26:06.900 --> 26:09.220
Don't tell me you want me
to ditch the wedding.

26:11.220 --> 26:12.620
Since you refuse to
call off the engagement,

26:13.530 --> 26:14.380
what's wrong

26:15.050 --> 26:15.940
with running?

26:16.250 --> 26:17.250
I told you.

26:17.810 --> 26:19.530
Luoying Valley keeps its word.

26:19.530 --> 26:21.620
Breaking a promise
is absolutely unthinkable.

26:21.620 --> 26:23.620
Besides, this marriage
was arranged by my aunt.

26:23.620 --> 26:24.570
I can afford to lose face,

26:24.570 --> 26:25.490
but she can't.

26:25.490 --> 26:26.420
So what?

26:27.290 --> 26:28.130
Forget it.

26:28.980 --> 26:30.570
I won't trouble you, Mr. Mu.

26:30.570 --> 26:33.380
If you still value our past friendship,

26:33.380 --> 26:34.770
tell me if you find out

26:34.770 --> 26:35.700
who it is later.

26:35.700 --> 26:37.180
If not, it's fine.

26:37.180 --> 26:38.770
I'll find out myself someday.

27:03.420 --> 27:05.700
Aunt, these persimmon cakes
are delicious.

27:05.700 --> 27:07.380
Let's buy more next time.

27:08.090 --> 27:09.660
These delicious persimmon cakes

27:09.660 --> 27:11.530
were sent by Aunt's good friends.

27:13.250 --> 27:14.900
But whether we'll receive more

27:15.810 --> 27:16.940
will depend on our luck.

27:17.660 --> 27:18.730
Speaking of which,

27:19.620 --> 27:21.420
it's been a long while
since I last saw them.

27:22.010 --> 27:23.660
When I grow up,

27:23.660 --> 27:25.770
I'll visit them on your behalf.

27:25.770 --> 27:27.090
They've already retreated to

27:27.090 --> 27:28.980
a place far, far away.

27:29.900 --> 27:31.620
I fear you won't get to see them.

27:39.570 --> 27:41.380
Elder Hu has been sent back
to the Li Sect.

27:41.380 --> 27:42.700
With your order, Mr. Mu,

27:42.700 --> 27:43.900
we can mobilize 100,000 sect members.

27:43.900 --> 27:45.050
And Nie Zhe will surely be found.

27:49.490 --> 27:50.330
Mr. Mu.

27:51.420 --> 27:52.260
Mr. Mu.

27:55.380 --> 27:56.380
Well, Shangguan,

27:57.050 --> 27:58.730
can't you use your head?

27:59.090 --> 28:00.700
Is now the time to talk about Nie Zhe?

28:01.250 --> 28:02.220
If not capturing Nie Zhe,

28:02.220 --> 28:03.290
what then?

28:03.290 --> 28:04.490
If we don't think of a plan soon,

28:04.490 --> 28:05.770
she'll be wed off.

28:09.220 --> 28:10.220
Mr. Mu, rest assured,

28:10.220 --> 28:11.420
I'll make sure

28:11.420 --> 28:13.900
Miss Cai's wedding falls through.

28:20.700 --> 28:22.620
Since Luoying Valley
can't break their promise,

28:25.380 --> 28:26.900
what about Peiqiong Manor?

28:30.280 --> 28:31.290
Mr. Mu, please take a look.

28:31.810 --> 28:33.900
This is the most beautiful courtesan
in Wu'an Town.

28:34.290 --> 28:36.420
I'll hire her with heavy gold

28:36.420 --> 28:38.420
to set a trap for Zhou Yuqi.

28:38.810 --> 28:39.810
You call this beauty?

28:40.620 --> 28:42.330
She's not even one-tenth
as pretty as Zhao.

28:42.770 --> 28:44.420
If Zhou Yuqi isn't blind,

28:44.420 --> 28:45.700
how could he leave Zhao for her?

28:46.090 --> 28:47.330
You're right, Mr. Mu.

28:47.940 --> 28:51.220
Miss Cai is a rare beauty.

28:51.220 --> 28:52.330
Of course, no one compares to her.

28:52.770 --> 28:53.770
But

28:53.770 --> 28:55.980
with my Seduction Powder,

28:55.980 --> 28:57.660
Zhou Yuqi will definitely submit.

28:57.660 --> 28:59.770
Mr. Mu, don't heed
Master You's foolish idea.

28:59.770 --> 29:01.620
If we drug him into losing his chastity,

29:01.620 --> 29:02.900
with Miss Cai's personality,

29:02.900 --> 29:04.140
she won't be angry.

29:04.140 --> 29:05.490
Instead, she'll think

29:05.490 --> 29:06.770
he's framed

29:06.770 --> 29:08.490
and pity him.

29:08.490 --> 29:10.380
It's a terrible plan,
not worth it at all.

29:10.380 --> 29:12.050
You have a better plan?

29:12.050 --> 29:12.890
Go on, let's hear it.

29:13.250 --> 29:14.730
Cut the mess clean and quick.

29:15.490 --> 29:16.330
Handle it directly.

29:19.050 --> 29:20.660
So that's your brilliant idea?

29:20.660 --> 29:21.730
If Miss Cai found out,

29:21.730 --> 29:23.290
she'll stab Mr. Mu right away.

29:23.290 --> 29:24.530
You call my idea terrible?

29:24.530 --> 29:26.420
Yours is worse than swill!

29:26.420 --> 29:27.380
Alright.

29:28.940 --> 29:30.050
For marriage,

29:34.860 --> 29:36.290
winning the heart comes first.

29:44.010 --> 29:45.620
Pack up after the ceremony.

29:45.620 --> 29:46.980
Leave for Qingque Sect tomorrow morning.

29:51.290 --> 29:52.130
Miss Cai.

29:53.050 --> 29:54.180
Shangguan Haonan.

29:54.660 --> 29:56.730
The Young Master
asks to talk to you in the side room.

29:56.730 --> 29:57.730
Nothing to talk about.

29:58.800 --> 30:00.700
The Young Master
mentioned the persimmon cakes...

30:04.660 --> 30:05.530
Then I'll go talk.

30:05.530 --> 30:06.420
I'll go with you.

30:07.490 --> 30:08.330
Mr. Song.

30:09.660 --> 30:11.490
The Young Master only invited Miss Cai.

30:11.490 --> 30:12.490
I must go.

30:12.490 --> 30:13.700
Then I'll have to intrude as well.

30:15.290 --> 30:16.380
It's all right, Yuzhi.

30:16.380 --> 30:18.050
I can go alone.

30:18.050 --> 30:18.890
Don't worry.

30:39.090 --> 30:39.930
Yeah.

30:40.180 --> 30:42.660
I hid the persimmon cakes from the tomb.

30:42.660 --> 30:43.810
Because I thought...

30:43.810 --> 30:45.700
You thought that persimmon cake
with six corners

30:46.250 --> 30:47.140
was extremely rare.

30:47.730 --> 30:48.570
Just now,

30:49.620 --> 30:50.700
why didn't you come over?

31:04.140 --> 31:05.570
Right and wrong must be kept apart.

31:05.570 --> 31:07.810
Besides, I'm already engaged.

31:07.810 --> 31:08.980
Of course, I should avoid suspicion.

31:09.570 --> 31:10.810
You're about to leave.

31:11.660 --> 31:12.980
Shouldn't you

31:12.980 --> 31:14.180
come and say goodbye to me?

31:23.420 --> 31:25.050
Not even a farewell drink?

31:25.490 --> 31:26.770
You came just to say farewell?

31:26.770 --> 31:27.770
Absolutely not.

31:29.090 --> 31:29.930
I said

31:30.250 --> 31:31.810
I'd pester you forever.

31:32.380 --> 31:33.620
Never let go.

31:39.250 --> 31:40.530
You want to marry someone else?

31:43.250 --> 31:44.700
Over my dead body.

31:45.940 --> 31:46.940
Madman.

32:20.810 --> 32:21.980
Wu'an Town has nice mountain goods.

32:22.380 --> 32:23.290
Buy some

32:23.290 --> 32:24.290
to take back tomorrow.

32:26.420 --> 32:27.530
Let's go check over there.

32:28.420 --> 32:29.260
Go!

32:31.770 --> 32:32.980
You shameless woman.

32:33.660 --> 32:35.860
You've been married to me
for over ten years.

32:35.860 --> 32:38.090
Yet you still pine for that man?

32:38.090 --> 32:40.860
Since your heart
still holds that Yuan guy,

32:41.250 --> 32:43.860
why did you marry me in the first place?

32:44.770 --> 32:47.180
You let me live for all these years as

32:47.180 --> 32:48.860
a man deceived and mocked!

32:51.250 --> 32:52.290
Look at this for yourself.

32:53.050 --> 32:55.090
What nonsense have you written here?

32:56.660 --> 32:58.940
(Cousin)
I'm going to settle this with him now!

32:59.380 --> 33:01.490
Don't! I do like him,

33:02.220 --> 33:03.730
but I married you

33:03.730 --> 33:06.180
because of my parents' orders.

33:06.660 --> 33:08.380
I'm sorry.

33:08.380 --> 33:10.010
I'll endure your blows and scolding.

33:10.010 --> 33:10.850
Get out!

33:11.660 --> 33:12.700
Get the hell out!

33:13.900 --> 33:15.010
Pei Zhisong.

33:15.010 --> 33:16.700
You heartless man!

33:19.180 --> 33:20.770
You sneaking seducer.

33:21.180 --> 33:22.380
You lecherous scumbag!

33:23.570 --> 33:25.010
Adulterers!

33:25.290 --> 33:26.130
Such disgrace.

33:26.420 --> 33:27.570
This is immoral.

33:27.570 --> 33:28.490
It is against all decorum.

33:31.570 --> 33:32.900
Back then, I was too timid.

33:33.490 --> 33:34.700
I didn't break off the engagement.

33:35.380 --> 33:37.220
And made you suffer so greatly.

33:38.250 --> 33:39.420
If I'd known this would happen,

33:40.090 --> 33:41.900
I never would've done it!

33:42.570 --> 33:43.770
How embarrassing!

33:48.050 --> 33:48.890
Xinrou!

33:49.810 --> 33:50.650
Xinrou!

33:51.140 --> 33:52.490
How can she be so unchaste?

33:57.180 --> 33:58.020
Xinrou!

33:58.900 --> 33:59.740
Yuqi.

34:00.180 --> 34:01.570
Xinrou, don't worry.

34:01.570 --> 34:03.940
I will have Mother
find you a good marriage.

34:03.940 --> 34:04.780
I will not marry!

34:05.700 --> 34:06.730
I will marry no one.

34:07.570 --> 34:09.130
I only ask that you don't drive me away.

34:09.610 --> 34:10.450
I know.

34:11.050 --> 34:12.650
After you marry Miss Cai,

34:13.030 --> 34:14.420
the Zhou clan won't have a place for me.

34:15.690 --> 34:16.980
When that day comes,

34:16.980 --> 34:18.130
I'll become a nun!

34:18.130 --> 34:19.210
How could there not be?

34:22.210 --> 34:23.340
As long as you're willing,

34:24.420 --> 34:26.740
the Zhou clan will always
have a spot for you.

34:27.740 --> 34:28.580
Yuqi,

34:29.570 --> 34:30.410
by then,

34:31.420 --> 34:33.010
you'll be powerless too.

34:33.940 --> 34:35.260
Don't worry about me.

34:35.940 --> 34:37.980
I'd rather live
a Life of Monastic Devotion,

34:38.380 --> 34:39.610
and for you and Miss Cai,

34:40.010 --> 34:41.170
pray for blessings all my life.

34:41.740 --> 34:42.580
Xinrou.

34:42.740 --> 34:43.610
Yuqi.

34:52.300 --> 34:53.420
Falling petals yearn.

34:54.170 --> 34:55.610
But the stream flows on.

34:56.010 --> 34:57.650
Yuqi, please stop trying to persuade me.

34:58.740 --> 35:00.090
My heart is as calm as still water.

35:11.420 --> 35:12.260
Xinrou.

35:17.050 --> 35:17.890
Xinrou!

35:21.530 --> 35:22.370
Ding.

35:22.740 --> 35:23.580
Fan.

35:30.690 --> 35:31.570
Young Lord Zhou.

35:32.540 --> 35:33.860
I've been talking to you all this time.

35:33.860 --> 35:35.050
Just to make one thing clear.

35:35.530 --> 35:37.010
Since ancient times,

35:37.010 --> 35:38.610
those who want it all,

35:39.010 --> 35:40.210
who play both sides

35:40.690 --> 35:41.900
never end well.

35:42.610 --> 35:44.090
Miss Min has no title,

35:44.090 --> 35:45.780
yet staying at the Zhou clan.

35:45.780 --> 35:48.010
It's really inappropriate,
don't you think?

35:48.010 --> 35:48.920
No way.

35:48.930 --> 35:49.980
I can't abandon Xinrou.

35:50.610 --> 35:52.090
Why can't you understand?

35:52.090 --> 35:53.260
Why won't you listen?

35:55.940 --> 35:56.820
Young Lord Zhou.

35:57.300 --> 35:59.010
Let me speak plainly
before anything else.

35:59.010 --> 36:01.210
Zhao belongs to all of us.

36:01.210 --> 36:03.690
If she suffers any grievance
after marriage,

36:03.690 --> 36:05.130
or if someone dares to mistreat her,

36:05.980 --> 36:08.170
we'll have no choice but to fight.

36:10.980 --> 36:11.820
Let's go.

36:42.540 --> 36:47.900
(Fortune-telling)

36:52.210 --> 36:53.050
Young Master.

36:54.900 --> 36:55.740
Young Master.

36:59.780 --> 37:00.860
Young Master, please wait.

37:01.690 --> 37:02.860
Sir, what is it?

37:03.940 --> 37:05.050
Looking at your face,

37:05.050 --> 37:06.340
your love line's dim,

37:06.340 --> 37:08.130
so relationships might be rough.

37:08.130 --> 37:09.980
And your forehead is dark,

37:09.980 --> 37:11.570
which points to pent-up worries.

37:11.570 --> 37:12.450
Why not

37:12.450 --> 37:13.610
tell me about it?

37:13.610 --> 37:15.900
I can help untangle your worries.

37:23.820 --> 37:24.660
Young Master Zhou.

37:26.130 --> 37:27.340
How did you know...

37:40.841 --> 37:51.501
=Generation to Generation=

38:10.261 --> 38:14.671
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:15.236 --> 38:19.851
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:20.191 --> 38:24.756
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

38:25.281 --> 38:29.581
♪Free to wander in the world♪

